                to identify them with certainty. This record refers to the prayer as attested in <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BDLaethf27"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: BDLaethf27</span></t:ref>.</t:p>
