            <t:div type="bibliography">
                <t:listBibl type="secondary">
                    <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/VD2T5WH4"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Worrell1914Zauberwesen"/><title level="a">Studien zum abessinischen Zauberwesen</title><title level="j">Zeitschrift für Assyriologie und verwandte Gebiete</title><author><forename>William Hoyt</forename><surname>Worrell</surname></author><date>1914_1915</date><biblScope unit="volume">29</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">85-141</biblScope><note type="url">http://menadoc.bibliothek.uni-halle.de/dmg/periodical/titleinfo/118379</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Worrell1914Zauberwesen</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Worrell1914Zauberwesen</note><t:citedRange>88</t:citedRange></t:bibl>
                </t:listBibl>
            </t:div>
            <t:div type="edition">
                <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" subtype="incipit">
                    <t:note>The following incipit is taken from <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BDLaethf27"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: BDLaethf27</span></t:ref>.</t:note>
                    <t:ab>
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩
                        አምላክ፡ ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ባርያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡ ርኩስ፡ ዘይሰልብ፡ ልበ፡ ሰብእ፡ ወያጸልም፡ አዕይንተ፡ ወይመጽእ፡ ከመ፡ ጽላሎት፡
                        በመዓልት፡ ወሕልም፡ አምሐለከ፡ ወአውግዝከ፡ በ፭ ቅንዋተ፡ መስቀሉ፡ 
                        ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሳዶር፡ አላዶር፡ ዳናት፡ አዴራ፡ ሮዳስ፡
                    </t:ab>
                </t:div>
                <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" subtype="explicit">
                    <t:note>The following explicit is taken from <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BDLaethf27"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: BDLaethf27</span></t:ref>.</t:note>
                    <t:ab>
                        እሰሮሙ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይቀረቡ፡ ወእለሂ፡ ቀርቡ፡ ይፃዑ፡ ዘሀለው፡ እመሂ፡ በሐቍ፡
                        ወእመሂ፡ በአቍያጽ፡ እመሂ፡ በአእደው፡ ወእመሂ፡ በአእጋር፡ ወበኵሉ፡ አካላት፡ ዘይቈረጥሙ፡ ወየሐምሙ፡ ወያመጽኡ፡ ንዋመ፡ በመዓልት፡ 
                        ወበሌሊት፡ ወያንቀጠቀጡ፡ ወኢይቅረቡ፡ ኀበ፡ ነፍሳ፡ ወሥጋሃ፡ ለአመትከ፡ 
                    </t:ab>
                </t:div>
            </t:div>
